title: 059 - BIG Bird Episode
description: On today's show, the guys get right into the folder of death which includes a new adversary in the cereal mascot deathmatch, sandhill cranes apparently being the sirloin of the sky, and several lists to pick from including one live concert, 2 appetizers, and how many of the 50 most common movies they've seen. The Boobz Brothers make another dynamite drop in plus the boys are joined by a very special surprise guest in studio.
